keywords={Behavioral research;  E-learning;  Personnel training;  Robot programming;  Robotics;  Robots, Breakings;  Digital literacies;  Estonia;  Gender challenge;  Glass ceiling;  Informatic strategy;  Master studies;  Pedagogy;  Teacher training;  Young peoples, Surveys},
funding_details={Ministry of DefenceMinistry of Defence, MOD},
